Clean-Room Rewrite Requirement (RFC-001):
  BaiLongma MIT-licensed components MUST undergo clean-room rewrite to
  maintain AGPL compliance. Team A reviews BaiLongma source and writes
  specifications; Team B implements from specifications without seeing
  original source. All SparkFox implementations based on BaiLongma concepts
  are original Rust/TypeScript clean-room rewrites.

